    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/MFollowill/status/2037641576734921008",
      "reply_text": "Yeah that versatility is what makes him a matchup nightmare. Can't wait to see it live tonight",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-27T23:38:24.569038+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/joy_ciana/status/2037645461972984248",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, KD's gravity is unmatched. He's always been a threat, even off the ball.",
